## ðŸ” Real-World Scenario

**Use Case**: Bimride wants to reduce fuel costs and delays by finding the shortest and fastest routes in high-density areas like Bridgetown.

**Solution**: Apply Dijkstraâ€™s algorithm using updated road graph data every 5 minutes.

